# 讀檔
dat_raw <- read_csv("04-weather-crime-pop.csv", show_col_types = FALSE)

# 整理時間排序
dat <- dat_raw %>%
  mutate(date = ym(sprintf("%d-%02d", year, month))) %>%
  arrange(city, date)

# 標記每個縣市的 NA 連續區間（run） ---
dat_runs <- dat %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  mutate(
    is_na = is.na(avg_temp),
    # 當 is_na 與前一筆不同就開新 run
    run_id = cumsum(coalesce(is_na != lag(is_na), TRUE))
  ) %>%
  ungroup()

# --- Step 2. 彙整「缺段報告」：只列出 is_na == TRUE 的區間 ---
na_segments <- dat_runs %>%
  filter(is_na) %>%
  group_by(city, run_id) %>%
  summarise(
    start_year  = first(year),
    start_month = first(month),
    end_year    = last(year),
    end_month   = last(month),
    start_date  = first(date),
    end_date    = last(date),
    n_months    = n(),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) %>%
  arrange(city, start_date)

write_csv(na_segments, "avg_temp_missing_segments_by_city.csv")
print(na_segments, n = 100)

# --- Step 3. 刪除整段缺值月份（= 把 avg_temp 為 NA 的列移除）---
dat_clean <- dat_runs %>%
  filter(!is_na) %>%            # 直接去掉所有 NA 區間的月份
  select(-is_na, -run_id) %>%
  arrange(city, date)

write_csv(dat_clean, "weather_crime_clean_no_avgtemp_gaps.csv")

# --- Step 4.每縣市跑 ADF：violent_crime_cases 與 avg_temp 各自檢定 ---
safe_adf <- function(x) {
  x <- as.numeric(x)
  x <- x[!is.na(x)]
  if (length(unique(x)) < 5) return(NA_real_)  # 太短或幾乎常數就略過
  out <- tryCatch(adf.test(x)$p.value, error = function(e) NA_real_)
  return(out)
}

adf_results <- dat_clean %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  summarise(
    adf_crime_p = safe_adf(violent_crime_cases),
    adf_temp_p  = safe_adf(avg_temp),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    crime_stationary = case_when(is.na(adf_crime_p) ~ "NA",
                                 adf_crime_p < 0.05 ~ "Stationary",
                                 TRUE ~ "Non-stationary"),
    temp_stationary = case_when(is.na(adf_temp_p) ~ "NA",
                                adf_temp_p < 0.05 ~ "Stationary",
                                TRUE ~ "Non-stationary")
  ) %>%
  arrange(city)

# === Step 5. 差分後做ADF ===

safe_adf <- function(x) {
  x <- as.numeric(x)
  x <- x[!is.na(x)]
  if (length(unique(x)) < 5) return(NA_real_)
  tryCatch(adf.test(x)$p.value, error = function(e) NA_real_)
}

adf_diff_results <- dat_clean %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  summarise(
    adf_diff_crime_p = suppressWarnings(safe_adf(diff(violent_crime_cases))),
    adf_diff_temp_p  = suppressWarnings(safe_adf(diff(avg_temp))),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    diff_crime_stationary = ifelse(!is.na(adf_diff_crime_p) & adf_diff_crime_p < 0.05, "Stationary", "Non-stationary"),
    diff_temp_stationary  = ifelse(!is.na(adf_diff_temp_p)  & adf_diff_temp_p  < 0.05, "Stationary", "Non-stationary")
  )

print(adf_diff_results, n = 22)

# === Step .6 Pearson's correlation ===
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)

dat_diff <- dat_clean %>%
  arrange(city, year, month) %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  mutate(
    diff_temp  = avg_temp - lag(avg_temp),
    diff_crime = violent_crime_cases - lag(violent_crime_cases)
  ) %>%
  filter(!is.na(diff_temp), !is.na(diff_crime)) %>%
  ungroup()

# 計算每個縣市的皮爾森相關係數
corr_results <- dat_diff %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  summarise(
    correlation = cor(diff_temp, diff_crime, method = "pearson"),
    p_value     = cor.test(diff_temp, diff_crime, method = "pearson")$p.value,
    .groups = "drop"
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    significance = case_when(
      p_value < 0.001 ~ "***",
      p_value < 0.01  ~ "**",
      p_value < 0.05  ~ "*",
      TRUE ~ ""
    )
  )
print(corr_results, n = 22)

# 視覺化（氣溫變化 vs 犯罪變化） 
library(sysfonts)

showtext_auto()

ggplot(dat_diff, aes(x = diff_temp, y = diff_crime)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.3, color = "steelblue") +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE, color = "firebrick") +
  facet_wrap(~ city, scales = "free", ncol = 4) +
  labs(title = "Δ Avg Temp vs Δ Violent Crime by City (Pearson Correlation)",
       x = "Change in Avg Temperature (°C)",
       y = "Change in Violent Crime Cases") +
  theme_minimal(base_size = 12)
